1. *Smatrao* sam da će danas biti kiša. (I *thought* it would rain today.)
2. On *smatra* da je ovo najbolji način da se to uradi. (He *believes* that this is the best way to do it.)
3. Da bi uspeli u ovom poslu, morate *smatrati* sve moguće opcije. (To succeed in this business, you have to *consider* all possible options.)
4. *Smatarajući* da je potrebno nešto promeniti, doneli su novu odluku. (By *considering* that something needed to be changed, they made a new decision.)
5. Oni su *smatrali* da su u pravu, ali su se na kraju ispostavili kao pogrešni. (They *thought* they were right, but in the end they turned out to be wrong.)
6. Kada *biste smatrali* da je neophodno, možete zatražiti dodatnu pomoć. (If you *considered* it necessary, you could ask for additional help.)
7. Nisam *smatrao* da će se to dogoditi tako brzo. (I didn't *think* it would happen so quickly.)
8. *Smatrajući se* najboljim učenikom u razredu, nije se trudio da bude još bolji. (By *considering himself* the best student in the class, he didn't try to be even better.)
9. *Smatrajmo* da će sve biti u redu, ako svi budemo radili zajedno. (Let's *assume* that everything will be fine if we all work together.)
10. Naš direktor *smatra* da je važno stalno unapređivati naše poslovanje. (Our director *believes* that it is important to constantly improve our business.)